name: Berserker's Call
desc: Axe taunts nearby enemy units, forcing them to attack him, while he gains bonus armor during the duration.

name: Impale
desc: Rock spikes burst from the earth along a straight path. Enemy units are hurled into the air, then are stunned and take damage when they fall.

name: Battle Trance
desc: Troll's presence on the battlefield increases the attack speed of himself and all allied heroes.

name: Rip Tide
desc: The Naga Siren and her images hit all nearby units with a damaging wave of water that lowers armor for 8 seconds.

name: Reincarnation
desc: Wraith King's form regroups after death, allowing him to resurrect when killed in battle.  Upon death, enemy units in a 900 radius will be slowed.\n\nUpgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.

name: Living Armor
desc: Infuses the target hero or structure with a protective coating which grants bonus regeneration. Also blocks some damage from all sources. Dispels when a number of damage instances are taken.

name: Concussive Shot
desc: Skywrath Mage sets off a long range shot that hits the closest hero within a long range.  Upon impact, it deals damage and slows in an area of effect.

name: Dispersion
desc: Damage done to Spectre is reflected on her enemies, leaving her unharmed. The effect lessens with distance.

name: Soul Catcher
desc: Captures the soul of a random enemy in an area, amplifies all damage they take. Units under the effect of Disruption can still be affected by Soul Catcher.

name: Searing Chains
desc: Ember Spirit unleashes fiery bolas that wrap around nearby enemies, anchoring them in place and dealing damage each second.
